data.description: Better than new! This exceptional 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and serene living, all set against the breathtaking backdrop of Arizona's majestic mountains. An open concept layout and gourmet kitchen is a perfect set up for a family dinner or hosting fun parties. Nicely upgraded with quartz counter tops, pendant lighting, beautiful accent walls throughout the house, luxury vinyl flooring, and a flex space which can be used for a play room or second living room. Nicely landscaped front and back adds to its appeal, and being situated at the end of a cul-de-sac with open space around is a great feature for privacy and tranquility. Your dream home is located in the picturesque community of Pronghorn Ranch, which offers many amenities including multiple pools, walking trails, and RV storage. This home is only one year old and ready for it's new owner.
